<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-10-22T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-10-22T13:00:00-05:00" n="567" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d567">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">811.24546/11: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Winant</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-10-22T19:00:00+01:00">October
                                    22, 1941—7 p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received October 22—2:38 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>5045. Regarding your 4458, October 15, 7 p.m. and your 4564, October 20,
                            1 p.m.<note n="11" xml:id="d567fn11">See footnote 6, <ref target="#pg_576">p. 576</ref>.</note> Eden told me this evening
                            that His Majesty’s Government agreed in principle and that they would
                            give me a memorandum on specific questions of detail tomorrow. This is
                            the third time that I have pressed this matter. Several Ministries are
                            concerned and the Foreign Office has not yet been able to obtain
                            complete clearance.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Winant</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>